### Notes:
* OpenGl works with the concpet of state machine.

* GLEW is an OpenGL Extension Wrangler Library

* OpenGL programmable pipeline:
Vertex Processor ----> Geometry Processor ----> Clipper ----> Rasterizer[Fragment Processor]

* Vertex Buffers -> stores vertices which contains positions, texture colors, etc. etc.

* Shaders -> A program loaded on to GPU

* Uniforms -> 



